original: Ågren, Sven Gustaf, disponent, Halmstad, f. 7/7/18 i Stockholm av kommendör Gustaf Å. o. Stina Berggren. — Anst. i Hand. A-B J. B. Berggren i Halmstad fr. 36, disp. fr. 45.^
translated: Ågren, Sven Gustaf, manager, Halmstad, b. 7/7/18 in Stockholm, son of Commander Gustaf Å. and Stina Berggren. - Employed at Hand. A-B J. B. Berggren in Halmstad from 1936, became manager in 1945.
